==English==
===Noun===
'''linesman'''
#{{football}} Previous name of a [[assistant referee]]
#{{tennis}} An [[official]] who [[call]]s [[shot]]s that [[pitch]] out of bounds, and [[judge]]s [[foot fault]]s
#{{icehockey}} An official whose primary task is to watch the [[blue line]] and determine when there has been an [[offside]]
#{{fb}} An official whose primary task is to determine if there has been a line of scrimmage violation
